<richard iii I.2.91>  Say that I slew them not?
<richard iii I.2.92>  Why, then they are not dead:
<richard iii I.2.93>  	But dead they are, and devilish slave, by thee.
<richard iii I.2.94>  I did not kill your husband.
<richard iii I.2.95>  Why, then he is alive.
<richard iii I.2.96>  Nay, he is dead; and slain by Edward's hand.
<richard iii I.2.97>  In thy foul throat thou liest: Queen Margaret saw
