<richard iii IV.1.92>  Poor heart, adieu! I pity thy complaining.
<richard iii IV.1.93>  No more than from my soul I mourn for yours.
<richard iii IV.1.94>  Farewell, thou woful welcomer of glory!
<richard iii IV.1.95>  Adieu, poor soul, that takest thy leave of it!
<richard iii IV.1.96>  	Go thou to Richmond, and good fortune guide thee!
<richard iii IV.1.97>  	Go thou to Richard, and good angels guard thee!
<richard iii IV.1.98>  	Go thou to sanctuary, and good thoughts possess thee!
