<richard iii IV.4.400>  	What canst thou swear by now?
<richard iii IV.4.401>  The time to come.
<richard iii IV.4.402>  That thou hast wronged in the time o'erpast;
<richard iii IV.4.403>  	For I myself have many tears to wash
